title: The Brotherhood IV: The Complex (2005) DVD RIP Gay Intrest
description:
From horror-meister David DeCoteau comes this creepy shocker about an age-old secret society's demonic plan to rule the world ... unless one man can stop it. Lee Hanlon (Sebastian Gacki), the smartest student at the elite military school the Complex, is intrigued by the academy's Black Skulls brotherhood but finds himself thrust into the role of global savior when he discovers their devilish origin. April Telek and Graham Kosakoski also star.

PG-13, 1 hr. 32 min.
